Stein Mart Inc.

1200 Riverplace Boulevard 
Jacksonville FL 32207 United States
Phone: +1 904-___-____
Fax: +1 904-___-____
http://www.steinmart.com





50
Managers




120
IT employees




$53.9MEST.
IT Budget




Stein Mart, Inc. is a fashion retailer offering a distinctive assortment of brand name and designer apparel, accessories and shoes for women and men and home fashions – all at savings of up to 60 percent off department store prices… MoreStein Mart, Inc. is a fashion retailer offering a distinctive assortment of brand name and designer apparel, accessories and shoes for women and men and home fashions – all at savings of up to 60 percent off department store prices every day. With some 280 shops in some 30 states, it sells off-price women's, men's, and children's brand-name clothing. Fashions range from casual to formal. Stein Mart also sells jewelry, handbags, linens, home decor, and gifts. Independent firms lease Stein Mart's shoe and fragrance departments.
Stein Mart, Inc. is a fashion retailer offering a distinctive assortment of brand name and designer apparel, accessories and shoes for women and men and home fashions – all at savings of up to 60 percent off department store prices… MoreStein Mart, Inc. is a fashion retailer offering a distinctive assortment of brand name and designer apparel, accessories and shoes for women and men and home fashions – all at savings of up to 60 percent off department store prices every day. With some 280 shops in some 30 states, it sells off-price women's, men's, and children's brand-name clothing. Fashions range from casual to formal. Stein Mart also sells jewelry, handbags, linens, home decor, and gifts. Independent firms lease Stein Mart's shoe and fragrance departments.

The IT department for Stein Mart Inc. oversees all IT strategy and a majority of procurement initiatives along with the long-term telecommunications outsourcing agreement. The company's outsourcing deal with Cass Information Systems, Inc, which was originally inked in 1999 and then expanded in 2009, provides them with automated telecommunication lifecycle and handling large location networks. 

The data warehousing team runs the Oracle-based data center and also leads the department in data storage, business intelligence (BI), and application development.The server environment is managed with SQL servers. Application development and programming are focused on improving the retail and business information for the company, while also working with outside vendors to improve the company's operations. The department handles the point of sale (POS) services and technology for the company. 

Enterprise infrastructure is also performed at the headquarters. It involves building and maintaining an IT infrastructure of hardware, networks and servers that is secure and meets SOX and PCI standards. IBM, Cisco, SharePoint, and Sun Solaris solutions make up the infrastructure.The help desk provides IT support services. 

Security and SOX compliance is also supervised by a manager at the headquarters.

The Project Management Office helps guide the company on strategies that will benefit business and also on the organization of a variety of projects, such as their enterprise application and telecommunication services. 

The IT budget is typically finalized in Q4.





